title: [Gisselle's Outfitting]
[Gisselle's General Store]
description: Plain wooden walls rise from an unfinished wooden floor.  Just above a worn rug hangs a tattered merchant permit, and an uneven wooden ceiling completes the picture.  A large cherrywood cabinet and a twisted dark metal rack stand side by side in the middle of the room.
